#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:14
msgid "Ajapaik is crowdsourcing additional metadata about pictorial heritage. Ajapaik is mostly hosting old photos, but there are also paintings, graphic art and historic films on Ajapaik."
msgstr "Tá Ajapaik ag bailiú meiteashonraí breise faoi oidhreacht phictiúrtha. Is iad seanghrianghraif is mó a bhíonn ar fáil ar Ajapaik, ach tá pictiúir, ealaín ghrafach agus scannáin stairiúla ar fáil ar Ajapaik chomh maith."

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:17
msgid "As an Ajapaik user you can"
msgstr "Mar úsáideoir Ajapaik is féidir leat"

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:19
msgid "geotag pictures in order to improve the location based search,"
msgstr "pictiúir geo-chlibeáilte chun an cuardach bunaithe ar shuíomh a fheabhsú,"

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:20
msgid "rephotograph historic pictures to create then-and-now picture pairs,"
msgstr "athghrianghrafadóireacht a dhéanamh ar phictiúir stairiúla chun péirí pictiúr a chruthú a bhí ann roimhe sin agus anois,"

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:21
msgid "tag persons on the pictures, add pictures to albums, categorize and comment pictures,"
msgstr "clibeanna a chur ar dhaoine ar na pictiúir, pictiúir a chur le halbaim, pictiúir a chatagóiriú agus trácht a dhéanamh orthu,"

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:22
msgid "transcribe handwritten messages on pictures or on the reverse sides of postcards,"
msgstr "teachtaireachtaí lámhscríofa a thras-scríobh ar phictiúir nó ar chúl cártaí poist,"

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:23
msgid "add historical imagery to Ajapaik – either by searching and importing from public collections or uploading yourself."
msgstr "cuir íomhánna stairiúla le Ajapaik – trí chuardach a dhéanamh agus iad a allmhairiú ó bhailiúcháin phoiblí nó trí iad a uaslódáil tú féin."

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:27
msgid "Ajapaik is a non-profit venture of the Estonian Photographic Heritage Society (MTÜ Eesti Fotopärand) that was created during a Garage48 hackathon in February 2011. Over the years Ajapaik has received grant funding but there is no permanent funding therefore we are very grateful if you can donate to <a href='/donate'>support us</a>."
msgstr "Is fiontar neamhbhrabúis de chuid Chumann Oidhreachta Grianghrafadóireachta na hEastóine (MTÜ Eesti Fotopärand) é Ajapaik a cruthaíodh le linn hackathon Garage48 i mí Feabhra 2011. Le blianta beaga anuas, fuair Ajapaik maoiniú deontais ach níl aon mhaoiniú buan ann, mar sin táimid an-bhuíoch dá bhféadfá síntiús a thabhairt chun <a href='/donate'>tacaíocht a thabhairt dúinn</a>."

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:31
#, python-format
msgid "Ajapaik has <b>%(total_photo_count)s</b> historic pictures, out of which <b>%(total_photos_tagged)s</b> pictures have been put on the map by <b>%(contributing_users)s</b> users and <b>%(rephoto_count)s</b> rephotographs for <b>%(rephotographed_photo_count)s</b> pictures made by <b>%(rephotographing_users)s</b> users."
msgstr "Tá <b>%(total_photo_count)s</b> pictiúr stairiúil ag Ajapaik, agus tá <b>%(total_photos_tagged)s</b> pictiúr curtha ar an léarscáil ag <b>%(contributing_users)s</b> úsáideoirí agus <b>%(rephoto_count)s</b> athghrianghraif do <b>%(rephotographed_photo_count)s</b> pictiúr déanta ag <b>%(rephotographing_users)s</b> úsáideoirí."

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:38
#, python-format
msgid "There are <b>%(person_annotation_count)s</b> faces detected on the pictures, a person has been identified in <b>%(person_annotation_count_with_person_album)s</b> cases, age or gender is marked for <b>%(person_annotation_count_with_subject_data)s</b> faces."
msgstr "Tá <b>%(person_annotation_count)s</b> aghaidheanna braite ar na pictiúir, tá duine aitheanta i <b>%(person_annotation_count_with_person_album)s</b> cásanna, tá aois nó inscne marcáilte do <b>%(person_annotation_count_with_subject_data)s</b> aghaidheanna."

#: ajapaik/ajapaik/templates/info/_general_info_modal_content.html:45
msgid "Overview of your own contributions can be found on your <a href='/me'>user profile page</a>."
msgstr "Is féidir forbhreathnú ar do chuid ranníocaíochtaí féin a fháil ar do <a href='/me'>leathanach próifíle úsáideora</a>."

